<div id="review_3009391677" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3009391677" />
    <a title="SJ" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/84858299-sj"><img alt="SJ" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1585105747p2/84858299.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3009391677?book_show_action=true">Jun 08, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="SJ" class="user" itemprop="url" name="SJ" href="/user/show/84858299-sj">SJ</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/84858299-sj?shelf=lgbtq">lgbtq</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
                  <em>
                    This review has been hidden because it contains spoilers. To view it,
                    <a href="#" onclick="Effect.toggle(&#39;reviewTextContainer3009391677&#39;); return false;">click here.</a>
                  </em>
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3009391677" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4720768906463735300">I liked this book. It was short and to the point which was both good and bad for me. I found pleasing aspects in both James &amp; Alex, but I feel like something was missing. The plot was predictable but very pleasant to read. The book as a whole is wholesome. It culminates to a happy ending for all the characters including first love, College acceptance, &amp; tightening family bonds.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


